Class ActuatorOfOnOffSwitch

java.lang.Object
smarthome.domain.actuator.ActuatorOfOnOffSwitch
All Implemented Interfaces:
AggregateRoot<ActuatorId>, DomainEntity<ActuatorId>, Actuator
public class ActuatorOfOnOffSwitch extends Object implements Actuator
This class represents an actuator of an on/off switch. It implements the Actuator interface.
